{"word":"συνεμβολή","slug":"συνεμβολή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n100047\" key=\"sunembolh/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">συνεμ-βολή</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n100047.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">throwing in together</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κώπης ῥοθιάδος ξ</foreign>. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the regular dip of all</tr_> the oars <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">together</tr_>, to the sound of the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κέλευσμα</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:396\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pers.\">Pers.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">396</biblScope> </bibl>:—in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:984\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">984</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πρυμνησίων ξυνεμβολάς</foreign> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Headlam</placeName>) may be read for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ξυνεμβόλοις</foreign>, in concrete sense the cables <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cast out</tr_> from the stern.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}